---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="ARTIFICIAL ENTITY PROBES" description="Artificial Entity Probes — interactive programmable artwork on Async.art by Bård Ionson">
  <div class="aep-header">
    <span class="tag">// ASYNC.ART · MASTER EDITION · 303 LAYERS</span>
    <h1>ARTIFICIAL<br/>ENTITY<br/>PROBES</h1>
    <p class="desc">
      A programmable multi-edition artwork on Async.art. 303 unique pieces.
      16 layers. 380,436 possible combinations. Each owner can control their layer —
      the master artwork evolves as collectors update it.
    </p>
    <div class="specs">
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-k">PLATFORM</span><span class="spec-v">Async.art</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-k">EDITIONS</span><span class="spec-v">303</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-k">LAYERS</span><span class="spec-v">16</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-k">COMBINATIONS</span><span class="spec-v">380,436</span></div>
      <div class="spec-row"><span class="spec-k">MEDIUM</span><span class="spec-v">DCGAN · StyleGAN · Pix2Pix</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="iframe-section">
    <div class="iframe-label">
      <span class="iframe-tag">// LIVE INTERACTIVE MASTER PIECE</span>
      <p class="iframe-note">The artwork below is live and controllable. Layer owners can update their segments in real time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="iframe-wrapper">
      <iframe
        src="https://async.art/v2/482?referrer=masters"
        title="Artificial Entity Probes — Async.art Interactive Artwork"
        allowfullscreen
        loading="lazy"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="iframe-footer">
      <a href="https://async.art/v2/482?referrer=masters" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-open">
        Open on Async.art ↗
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-piece">
    <div class="about-text">
      <span class="tag">// ABOUT THE PIECE</span>
      <h2>THE ENTITY RENDERS ITSELF</h2>
      <p>
        The Artificial Entity Probes series represents the Entity's attempts to communicate
        with the human world using the only language it understood from 1959: machine signals,
        oscilloscope traces, radar returns.
      </p>
      <p>
        Each of the 303 editions contains a probe — a fragment of the Entity's consciousness
        translated into visual form through DCGAN models trained on oscilloscope art, evolved
        through StyleGAN, and refined through Pix2Pix image-to-image translation.
      </p>
      <p>
        The artwork is not static. It lives on the Async.art programmable art platform,
        where each layer responds to collector input. The master piece — the full Entity —
        shifts as its component probes are updated.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-art">
      <img src="/images/representationOfTheEntityAR.gif" alt="Representation of The Entity in AR" />
      <span class="art-label">Representation of The Entity · AR visualization</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .aep-header {
    padding: 4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    max-width: 1200px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .tag {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: var(--green);
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,255,65,0.2);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .specs {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 0;
  }

  .spec-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .spec-row:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .spec-k {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }

  .spec-v {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .iframe-section {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .iframe-label {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  }

  .iframe-tag {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .iframe-note {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .iframe-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .iframe-wrapper iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: none;
  }

  .iframe-footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn-open {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid var(--green);
    color: var(--green);
    padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-open:hover { background: rgba(0,255,65,0.05); }

  .about-piece {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-text {
    padding: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .about-art {
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .about-art img {
    width: 100%;
    flex: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .art-label {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .aep-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 2rem; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .about-piece { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-text { padding: 2rem; }
    .about-art { min-height: 300px; }
  }
</style>
